H0.text: The major UK/European mobile network corp EE was originally branded. Orange

H1.text: The major UK/European mobile network corp EE was originally branded. T-Mobile

H2.text: The major UK/European mobile network corp EE was originally branded. Everything Everywhere

H3.text: The major UK/European mobile network corp EE was originally branded. 4GEE

A4.text: EE was formed following the merger of T-Mobile UK and Orange UK

A5.text: Orange and Deutsche Telekom merged their UK businesses in 2010 to form a joint venture branded as EE

A6.text: T-Mobile UK, a former UK mobile phone network operator which merged with the former Orange UK to create EE
